  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Recently \"Save password until logout\" (https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/5617) was implemented for iOS. This issue is about doing the same for Android. More details can be found in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/5617.\r\n\r\n\r\n### TODO\r\n\r\n- [x] Discuss the password storage options // @corpetty @rasom @mandrigin \r\n- [x] Implement minimum security guarantee in react-native-keychain\r\n- [x] Enable storing password with `TEE` guarantee on Android\r\n- [ ] Hash password before using it and implement the migration",
